Self maintained dwm with some nice patches

I bet it's the most ELEGANT window manager you've ever seen!

******************
*  Requirements  *
******************
Xlib header files.
( There might be some other libs needed that I can only recall when seeing installation errors.
((So feel free to commit any issue


******************
*  Installation  *
******************
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dwm is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dwm

    make clean install (as root)
